{"tid":497401,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 一齊研究點樣去爭取更合理賠償","createTime":"2017-12-12T16:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T04:31:28.000Z","uid":155763,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7a839d991fe205e86e82ae43299ce4e9d171492b","tid":497401,"uid":155763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T16:58:41.000Z","msg":"原本小弟12月8號坐KLM由英國出發經荷蘭返去香港，原定9號中午到香港，跟著夜晚就去睇側田尾場演唱會。點知黑仔都爆，無啦啦臨半個鐘頭前上機飛去荷蘭個時收到email話荷蘭去香港個班機因為被雷劈中，cancel左。之後佢地安排我搭去吉隆坡再返香港，結果比原定抵達時間遲成10個鐘有多。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/000928_154b4d69d7c63f0fa75990fd1ada5978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F000928_154b4d69d7c63f0fa75990fd1ada5978.jpg&h=c4e769a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/000928_3ab92f199eaa63c427a5fd659eaed1d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F000928_3ab92f199eaa63c427a5fd659eaed1d4.jpg&h=6b3c8463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，折磨左成日，演唱會已經無得睇，本身已經好失望。點知之後去攞行李個陣，小喇叭，我個行李竟然寄失埋，問返機場行李中心話無record，唔知去q左邊，我個下真係呆撚咗，真係好無助。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然行李過兩日之後送上門，但係始終有d心靈創傷。見到行李上邊個馬來西亞航空個tag應該喺吉隆坡運過黎，咁其實件行李個晚無上到機係KLM定港龍責任呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/002620_000f2a9954cc59b9d90eb31a1c55c518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F002620_000f2a9954cc59b9d90eb31a1c55c518.jpg&h=d4cbacc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我就上KLM個網claim佢，諗住攞下賠償。點知佢地話行李個d佢地唔會賠。跟著個飛機cancellation又話因為天氣因素而唔關佢事。不過就話因為搞到我無演唱會睇，所以可憐我，就是但賠5000miles算數。<br />\n<br />\n行李email回覆：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/003207_d1f5e055076786c56a1982d773918369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F003207_d1f5e055076786c56a1982d773918369.jpg&h=57b32e47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/003208_d1f5e055076786c56a1982d773918369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F003208_d1f5e055076786c56a1982d773918369.jpg&h=8f3e4bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班次取消email回覆：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/003256_9c33272041af8425269339a2aa8e41b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F003256_9c33272041af8425269339a2aa8e41b5.jpg&h=f44c6e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/003257_9c33272041af8425269339a2aa8e41b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F003257_9c33272041af8425269339a2aa8e41b5.jpg&h=1c5bfeba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我去睇下5000miles值幾錢，點知原來得個d爛鬼行李牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最巴閉個個係唔知咩俾你去睇醫生。言下之意啫係小弟個10個鐘只係值一塊幾廿蚊嘅行李牌，簡直係侮辱緊人，直頭被佢地當狗咁撚。大佬呀，我張側田飛都要780一張，仲要send埋俾佢地做證據，都可以咁孤寒成咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/004213_aecccabeda1cbb926a6ab0e019c267e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F004213_aecccabeda1cbb926a6ab0e019c267e8.jpg&h=e7d3b9be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/004226_d6b2dd4cddd5eac1d64085c2ed3cc480.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F004226_d6b2dd4cddd5eac1d64085c2ed3cc480.jpg&h=c13c5ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/004245_bec86c5e87b1b42c097a086888649b8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F004245_bec86c5e87b1b42c097a086888649b8c.jpg&h=dea1a465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身唔諗住開post，諗住今次坐商務都可能有一千幾百賠下，但係見到個賠償真係幾唔合理，所以就開post同巴打商量下有咩對策，爭取合理d嘅賠償。小弟今次係第一次坐KLM，坦白講d服務真係唔錯，但係呢件事令我對佢地嘅印象真係幾反感。所以小弟亦都想分享下我今次嘅經歷，睇下巴打有咩意見，之後再睇下其他巴打有咩慘既經歷都可以一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03aa363b21b8ea9f99f3c26b5053eabcb5311248","tid":497401,"uid":56466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"之前搭俄羅斯航空由瑞士飛莫斯科飛返香港，因為落大雪，miss左莫斯科飛香港果班，搞到係莫斯科飛左去北京再轉香港航空返黎，遲左6，7個鐘咁，件行李就第二日先到，送上門咁<br />\n買果個保險好似唔夠8個鐘冇得賠"},{"pid":"790b863f2e27e92a9c5334a5d3401dc231b6bd91","tid":497401,"uid":155763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前搭俄羅斯航空由瑞士飛莫斯科飛返香港，因為落大雪，miss左莫斯科飛香港果班，搞到係莫斯科飛左去北京再轉香港航空返黎，遲左6，7個鐘咁，件行李就第二日先到，送上門咁<br />\n買果個保險好似唔夠8個鐘冇得賠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實呢d情況無得賠係好正常？"},{"pid":"8e7b4e335745586d33d88f87fed52c23bb933085","tid":497401,"uid":4357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"歐盟境內出發嘅機delay唔係一定有得賠50歐咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01085778281b503512572e5d9ce1e5e728acd1e7","tid":497401,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T18:15:32.000Z","msg":"有D錢真係唔好慳，坐英航/維珍航空好過"},{"pid":"21b93d1e0b3bacbcba0ea09117dfd9412bd46403","tid":497401,"uid":30587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T19:10:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flight_Compensation_Regulation_261/2004#Applicability\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFlight_Compensation_Regulation_261%2F2004%23Applicability&d=ZUEwTQyDNCO0O%2BjS2JMtiARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c88fc80c\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flight_Compensation_Regulation_261/2004#Applicability</a><br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cd141229e70648f206a295973d269c3ca98407","tid":497401,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T19:54:18.000Z","msg":"klm啲位好逼"},{"pid":"2cfa97e106d9d0c594ea51fce21dec6b87e90257","tid":497401,"uid":155763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T23:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flight_Compensation_Regulation_261/2004#Applicability\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFlight_Compensation_Regulation_261%2F2004%23Applicability&d=ZUEwTQyDNCO0O%2BjS2JMtiARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c88fc80c\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flight_Compensation_Regulation_261/2004#Applicability</a><br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知呢條歐盟法例，不過佢地就係話因為自然因素影響從而無得賠。我都係希望賠番張演唱會門票價錢打個和算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f692d2c46a41e0162f5ad08fb9cea464127576","tid":497401,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:08:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flight_Compensation_Regulation_261/2004#Applicability\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFlight_Compensation_Regulation_261%2F2004%23Applicability&d=ZUEwTQyDNCO0O%2BjS2JMtiARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c88fc80c\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flight_Compensation_Regulation_261/2004#Applicability</a><br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知呢條歐盟法例，不過佢地就係話因為自然因素影響從而無得賠。我都係希望賠番張演唱會門票價錢打個和算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n被雷劈又真係自然因素 的確係冇得賠喎"},{"pid":"f7d39af5513bdece032106931660e413e4424e32","tid":497401,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:23:56.000Z","msg":"認真，都冇沒可以賠比你"},{"pid":"df94208a3a6f07969da1c3ac9e02771188eb91df","tid":497401,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:29:12.000Z","msg":"有無拎延遲證明？寫咩原因？<br />\n如果真係雷擊，claim唔到euro flight compensation"},{"pid":"617db469cffc92bfc2c98b4680299a961c2de317","tid":497401,"uid":40550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:33:37.000Z","msg":"保險有, 航空公司無<br />\n<br />\n而家因為大雪STUCK左係北道覆你"},{"pid":"809bb8a02962683f832419919d00e1e22595cf1d","tid":497401,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:36:14.000Z","msg":"佢搵到轉機path俾你已經好俾面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你搭完機之後既活動其實唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦因為真係天氣問題而唔係壞機，在理上佢唔賠亦吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你俾因航佢覆個 template俾你咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDear Mr Kuroda<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThank you for contacting us. Your feedback is extremely important to us as it gives us an opportunity to improve our services.<br />\n<br />\nI am sorry about your recent experience with us. etc etc etc"},{"pid":"207d9d0e176a9079c63d264d776c8961a99a0c3b","tid":497401,"uid":1841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:16:02.000Z","msg":"又一香港狗無理投訴<br />\n同支那人冇分"},{"pid":"9e9c4867f9487aa2bc7e601fe5d005a0af7bf837","tid":497401,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:28:22.000Z","msg":"claim保險啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d96c8ea1245b6603f2b516bd72dbde862b54edf","tid":497401,"uid":157153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:33:39.000Z","msg":"吊你老母 你條廢柴除左識投訴R著數 仲識D乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廁田狗都唔睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209adef959e1d7d3fca4cf266275fcda8b4b709b","tid":497401,"uid":155763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無拎延遲證明？寫咩原因？<br />\n如果真係雷擊，claim唔到euro flight compensation</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無拎，我小出門，第一次遇到呢d問題，都預左飛機取消個個claim會無得賠。之前打電話話係雷劈，屬於自然因素，但係佢地個邊話有得賠，所以就試下。不過行李個邊我諗住chur下佢地，話哂都叫做人為失誤。"},{"pid":"2306950941e294724861e99f3b3f5293f8ae8c72","tid":497401,"uid":155763,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>claim保險啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無買到保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7784cbe5ff425ad13c307fc0e2f4f610a2462ce0","tid":497401,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:10:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>claim保險啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無買到保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e40f329c3077bbed21ce3682700b4bcc81ae4c","tid":497401,"uid":155763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquo